*xbmc-13.1 (29 Jun 2014)

  29 Jun 2014; Stijn Tintel (stintel) <stijn+gentoo@linux-ipv6.be>
  -xbmc-13.0_p2-r1.ebuild, +xbmc-13.1.ebuild, +files/generate.sh:
  Version bump. Add generate.sh from upstream ebuild.

  29 Jun 2014; Stijn Tintel (stintel) <stijn+gentoo@linux-ipv6.be>
  xbmc-13.0_p2-r1.ebuild:
  Depend on sys-power/upower or sys-power/upower-pm-utils when udev USE flag is
  set.

  29 Jun 2014; Stijn Tintel (stintel) <stijn+gentoo@linux-ipv6.be>
  xbmc-12.3-r1.ebuild, xbmc-13.0_p2-r1.ebuild:
  Fix USE dependency on media-libs/libsdl, "audio" USE flag was renamed to
  "sound".

*xbmc-13.0_p2-r1 (12 May 2014)

  12 May 2014; Stijn Tintel (stintel) <stijn+gentoo@linux-ipv6.be>
  +xbmc-13.0_p2-r1.ebuild, -files/xbmc-9.11-jpeg7-performance.diff,
  -files/xbmc-9.11-smartplaylist-deletelastrule.diff,
  -files/xbmc-9.11-wavpack.patch, files/xbmc-9999-nomythtv.patch,
  -files/playercontrol_partymode_fix.diff,
  -files/xbmc-fix-mysql-memoryleak.diff, metadata.xml:
  media-tv/xbmc: Version bump. Based on upstream xbmc-13.0_p2.ebuild, with
  Samba4 compat. Clean up old patches.

*xbmc-12.2-r2 (11 Jul 2013)

